com.ibm.team.workitem.common.model

Interface IWorkItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IAuditable, IAuditableHandle, IItem, IItemHandle, IManagedItem, IManagedItemHandle, IProjectScoped, IWorkItemHandle

    public interface IWorkItem
extends IWorkItemHandle, IAuditable, IProjectScoped
    A work item represents a piece of work in a certain state (like new, in progress, done). Various built-in attributes are provided and additional custom attributes can be added.
    Since:
    0.5

        void addCustomAttribute(IAttribute attribute)
        Adds the given custom attribute to the work item. The work item must not have the attribute already and the attribute must have a supported type.

        Clients should initialize the attribute to either a specific value or its default value.

        Parameters:
        attribute - the custom attribute
        See Also:
